text: Laidy Yorveys Gómez Flórez (born 12 December 1981) is a Venezuelan politician, a member of Democratic Action and the current governor of Táchira. Gómez was born in Rubio, Junín Municipality, Táchira, Venezuela, and became the governor of Táchira in 2017. == References == Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Governors of Táchira Category:People from Rubio, Venezuela Category:Democratic Action (Venezuela) politicians Category:Members of the National Assembly (Venezuela) Category:Venezuelan women lawyers Category:Venezuelan women in politics
